heading: September 11 Terrorist Attacks, 2001.
alt-heading: World Trade Center (New York, N.Y.). Terrorist Attack, 2001.
general-note: Here are entered works on the attacks by terrorists on the World Trade Center in New York City and the Pentagon outside Washington, D.C., using three hijacked commercial jetliners, and on the crash of a fourth hijacked jetliner in a rural area of Pennsylvania on September 11, 2001..
